(1, 10, NULL, 'Southwest Airlines Name Change Policy', 'southwest-airlines-name-change-policy', 'Passenger often fills wrong initials on the ticket and create trouble for themselves. These mistakes can create inconvenience if not rectified on time. Every airline provides the facility to makeÂ name corrections on tickets for easy boarding. Likewise, Southwest Airlines also offers name change services that you can use for correcting the essential initials of your name.', 'Southwest Airlines Ticket Name Change/Correction Policy', 'If you want to change the passenger name, here is the Southwest Airlines name change policy and process to correct or change your name on the flight ticket.', 'Southwest Airlines flying plane', '<p>Passenger often fills wrong initials on the ticket and create trouble for themselves. These mistakes can create inconvenience if not rectified on time. Every airline provides the facility to make&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on tickets</strong> for easy boarding. Likewise, Southwest Airlines also offers name change services that you can use for correcting the essential initials of your name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Southwest Airlines provides convenience to passengers by preparing guidelines for a name change. Customers can smoothly correct or change their names by using these guidelines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Southwest Airlines Name Change Policy Guidelines</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the guidelines that every traveler has to follow for name correction on Southwest Airlines tickets:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger cannot change their name to transfer the ownership of tickets to another person. In this case, a traveler can transmit a ticket by canceling the flight and rebooking again.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A traveler cannot change the name. Therefore, you can correct only a few characters of your first, middle, and last name.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger is allowed to correct a name up to four characters. The four characters in total for first, middle, and last names are allowed.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The name change is only allowed in the case of legal circumstances such as marriage or divorce.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The customer&#39;s name must match the government-issued identification cards.</li>\r\n	<li>A traveler is allowed to change the name only once.</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger must provide proper documents to the airline for a legal name change.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of an interline or codeshare agreement, the name change request of the Southwest flight segment will be permitted.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Once the&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong> process is completed, a passenger must select the seats again. The customer cannot swap the seats from the old to the new PNR.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Southwest Airlines Name Corrections on the Tickets</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Flying with the correct name is Southwest Airlines&rsquo;s primary condition. If minor errors are in your name, you can correct them under the Southwest Airlines name change policy. Making necessary rectifications in your name is part of the name correction policy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/name-change/southwest-airlines-name-change-policy\" target=\"_self\">Southwest Airlines name change policy</a> does not allow a passenger to change the full name. Also, a customer is not permitted to&nbsp;<strong>add the name</strong> of another person to the ticket. However, a person is authorized to change the name due to marriage or divorce. Southwest Airlines permits a person to change the name after marriage only on the submission of legal documents.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important to note that in the case of marriage or divorce, a passenger is only allowed to correct the last name. The following documents are needed at the time of name correction on tickets:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In the event of a marriage, a traveler has to provide a marriage license, previous identity proof, and existing identification proof.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of divorce, a passenger must submit court orders and documents supporting a legal name change.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Ways of Name Correction on the Tickets of Southwest Airlines</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Every passenger uses different methods for solving their misspelled errors on the tickets. For this, Southwest Airlines has provided distinct ways of correcting the name. So, a passenger can change the name on the ticket in the following ways:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 1 - Name Change by Calling the Airlines</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Every airline provides contact information to passengers that they can use anytime. Most customers use these details to modify the name on the ticket. After you call the customer service number, follow the given steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You must have your six-digit booking number.</li>\r\n	<li>Submit photocopies of legal documents or any other information that depicts your correct identity when asked by the representative.</li>\r\n	<li>You can only add up to four characters in total to your first, middle, and last name.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If there is any fee alongside the fare difference to be paid, you must pay that.</li>\r\n	<li>After the&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>, you will get a new confirmation. Next, you need to complete the check-in and seat selection again.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 2 - Name Correction by Using Website</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A customer can use the Southwest Airlines website to alter the name on the ticket. If you want to use this method for rectifying the name on Southwest Airlines, you need to go along with the following steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First, stop by the official site of the airline.</li>\r\n	<li>Second, click on the &ldquo;log in&rdquo; icon.</li>\r\n	<li>Third, fill in your confirmation number and last name.</li>\r\n	<li>Fourth, click on the flight button.</li>\r\n	<li>Fifth, select &ldquo;manage reservation&rdquo; from the menu.</li>\r\n	<li>Sixth, you will get on the scheduled reservation table, where you will get an option of &ldquo;Edit Name&rdquo;. Edit your name and enter all the relevant information regarding the name change.</li>\r\n	<li>Seventh, you will pay the fee, if applicable.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, save all the information and wait for the confirmation of the new ticket.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 3 - Name Change on the Ticket Via Compliant Page</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The compliant page is the unique feature of Southwest Airlines name change policy. It informs the airline about a passenger&rsquo;s complaints and can be used for placing requests.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the steps to use this method for name correction:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First, visit the contact us page on Southwest Airlines&rsquo; <a href=\"https://www.southwest.com/\" target=\"_blank\">website</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>Second, use the Email Us option given on the page.</li>\r\n	<li>Third, fill the form with the necessary details, like flight particulars.</li>\r\n	<li>Fourth, upload the relevant documents in support of the name change.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, wait for the response that you may receive on your email ID.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Southwest Airlines Name Change Charges</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The name change fee depends on the situation under which the request is initiated. If a passenger has started the&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> request within 24 hours, there is no need to pay any change fee.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, if you have requested the name correction after 24 hours of booking, you may have to pay between $80-$200. The fee amount is calculated depending on the date of change and the time left for boarding the flight.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the name correction, the ticket will be re-issued in the same available or higher class. If the ticket is rebooked in the higher class of service, then you will also have to pay the fare difference.&nbsp;</p>', '921262.webp', NULL, '2022-10-31 18:21:28'),
(2, 10, NULL, 'Alaska Airlines Name Change Policy', 'alaska-airlines-name-change-policy', 'Making errors while booking a flight is a frequent affair. A passenger makes foolish spelling mistakes while typing the name. However, there are cases of name change due to reasons other than incorrect spelling or initials. In such cases, a traveler may want to apply for aÂ name change on the boarding pass.', 'Alaska Airlines Name Change on Ticket | +1-800-865-1848', 'Alaska Airlines Name Correction Policy provides the simplest ways to replace or correct your name online. Learn more about the passenger name change.', 'Alaska Airlines flying plane', '<p>Making errors while booking a flight is a frequent affair. A passenger makes foolish spelling mistakes while typing the name. However, there are cases of name change due to reasons other than incorrect spelling or initials. In such cases, a traveler may want to apply for a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are flying with Alaska Airlines, you can easily change your incorrect name on the ticket with the help of its name change policy. It provides various methods to make corrections or changes in the name on the flight ticket. Therefore, understanding the name change policy of Alaska Airlines can help you overcome the obstacles while boarding the flight with the wrong details.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Name Change on Flight Tickets Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The name change policy of Alaska Airlines defines several rules and regulations for making corrections to the name on flight tickets. Alaska Airlines asks its passengers to write the correct name on the ticket. The policy offers several approaches through which a customer can modify the name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alaska Airlines&nbsp;<strong>name change on flight tickets</strong> policy adheres to the rules mentioned under this policy. As per the policy, the airlines facilitate a passenger with the name change process. The traveler must know the circumstances under which the name can be rectified.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the conditions under which a passenger can alter the wrong name:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A customer must have legal documents for modifying the last name after marriage or divorce.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A traveler can request for change in the letters in your name.</li>\r\n	<li>Passengers can invert their names.</li>\r\n	<li>A customer can complete the first names if written in short forms.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The <a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/name-change/alaska-airlines-name-change-policy\">Alaska Airlines name change policy</a> also allows the change in the middle name.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Flight Name Change Due to Legal Reasons</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Alaska Airlines allows a passenger to modify the name on the ticket in case of marriage or divorce. In such cases, only the surname or last name of the passenger is allowed to change. You may have to submit the legal documents to the airline in support of the name change.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the name change request to process further, the operator may ask you to submit the following documents:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In the event of a marriage, you have to submit existing proof of identity, a marriage certificate, or previous evidence of identification.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of divorce, you must submit the judicial orders and the piece of legal information.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Name Correction on Reservation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>To fly with Alaska Airlines, it is necessary that every traveler board the plane with the correct name spellings on the ticket. If the passenger fails to do so, he/she may face inconvenience during the flight boarding. Therefore, use the name correction policy of Alaska Airlines to avoid last-minute hassle. With the help of this policy, you can rectify minor errors in your name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Passenger Name Change Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A traveler cannot change the complete name on the Alaska Airlines ticket. You are not permitted to transfer the ticket to another person by changing the name on the air ticket. If you want to&nbsp;<strong>add the name</strong> of another person, you need to cancel the reservation first. Further, you can book a new reservation with that person&rsquo;s name.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Change Name on Alaska Airlines Flight Ticket?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Alaska Airlines name change policy provides online and offline methods for a name change or corrections. A passenger can modify the name on the ticket with the help of provisions mentioned under the policy. You can choose any of the following methods for&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the reservation</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 1 - Change Name Via Alaska Airlines Website</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Using the website for changing the name is the simplest way. You can use this method online to correct minor errors in spelling. You must accompany the following steps to proceed with the name corrections under this method:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Visit the Alaska Airlines official <a href=\"https://www.alaskaair.com/\" target=\"_blank\">site</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>Next, tap the &ldquo;Manage Booking&rdquo; option on the home page.</li>\r\n	<li>Fill in the necessary details like Passenger&rsquo;s Last Name, Confirmation Code, and E-ticket number.</li>\r\n	<li>Tap on the &ldquo;Continue&rdquo; button.</li>\r\n	<li>The complete booking details will be open in front of you.</li>\r\n	<li>Follow the &ldquo;Change Name&rdquo; option and make the necessary corrections in the name.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, print the ticket with the correct initials.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: You cannot change more than three characters in your name through this online method.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are a few conditions that you must satisfy to be able to change the name through the online method. You must adhere to the following requirements given under the Alaska Airlines name change policy for making corrections:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger&rsquo;s ticket must be brought with Alaska Airlines directly, not through a travel agency or any other source.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The ticket must not include any discounts or government offers.</li>\r\n	<li>The reservation should not be a group ticket. Also, there should not be more than seven members included in a booking.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The flight segments of your ticket should not consist of more than 8 arrangements.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A traveler&rsquo;s booking should not comprise any kind of special accommodations like pets or other requests.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The tickets purchased with Mileage plan awards should not be eligible for any kind of change. Only&nbsp;<strong>name corrections of general reservations</strong> are acceptable.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 2 - Change Name Via Customer Care</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are less aware of the online procedure, you can use the traditional mode of modifying the name on the ticket. Alaska Airlines offers a convenient means for correcting the name on the ticket. In this method, you can contact the customer care representatives of Alaska Airlines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The customer care number will connect you with the agents of Alaska Airlines. Once you get in touch with the airlines, you will mention the reason for contacting them. If you want to change the name, you must tell the correct purpose, like marriage or divorce.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Further, provide the necessary details about your reservation, including the travel date, aircraft number, and boarding pass details. The agent will confirm your information and proceed with the name change process. This method is also best for making last minutes changes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 3 - Change Name Via Airport Kiosk</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Another mode of&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on the ticket</strong> is by using Airport Kiosk. The Kiosk is a self-service device that allows passengers to perform various activities. With the help of the Kiosk, you can print boarding passes, upgrade seating options, and modify the name on the ticket.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The passenger can use this service at the airport. It allows a passenger to alter or change the name without following a tedious process:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You can click the &ldquo;Change Flights&rdquo; option on the Kiosk machine.</li>\r\n	<li>Then, open the flight itinerary.</li>\r\n	<li>Further, provide the essential details regarding the reservation.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, click on the name that you want to modify and enter the new name to finish the process.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This self-operated machine saves a lot of effort and makes the process simple. The Kiosk method is also the most reliable as it leaves no chance of errors. It is the most efficient method of&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on the reservation</strong> under Alaska Airlines as the airline officials confirm the name change themselves. Also, you can ask for assistance if you face any issues while operating the machine.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Limitations of Alaska Airlines Name Change</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Alaska&#39;s name-change policy may not work for travelers. In such instances, a passenger should know the limitations before requesting the name change. Following are the limitations that you should be aware of before:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The passenger&rsquo;s name on the ticket should match the name on the government-issued identification card. If there is a mismatch between the names, then it may create trouble during boarding.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If the name mentioned on the passport is incorrect, you should first rectify it. After that, you should request the&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Name Correction Fees</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alaska Airlines name change policy may charge fees for allowing corrections or changes on the ticket. Although, you can avoid the costs if you make the changes within 24 hours of the ticket reservation. If you apply for a name change after 24 hours, you will be charged $125. The fees remain similar for every change or correction in the name.&nbsp;</p>', '799900.webp', NULL, '2022-10-31 18:22:16'),
(5, 10, NULL, 'Delta Airlines Name Change Policy', 'delta-airlines-name-change-policy', 'TheÂ name change on the boarding pass is a common phenomenon in the aviation industry. Numerous passengers apply for a name change because of multiple reasons. Like any other airline, the legal requirement of Delta Airlines is that every passenger should fly with the correct name.', 'Delta Airlines Name Correction on Ticket Policy ,Rules', 'With Delta Airlines name change policy, you can correct your wrong name on the flight ticket. Learn how to change the passenger name on the ticket.', 'Delta Airlines flying plane', '<p>The&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong> is a common phenomenon in the aviation industry. Numerous passengers apply for a name change because of multiple reasons. Like any other airline, the legal requirement of Delta Airlines is that every passenger should fly with the correct name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delta Airlines recognizes the significance of name correction and offers many options. They ease and accelerate the name change process to protect the customer&rsquo;s interest. Therefore, a passenger will not distress before requesting a change.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Here are the following conditions that you must satisfy to be allowed to do name correction on tickets</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Delta Airlines authorizes the change of the last name ensuing from marriage.</li>\r\n	<li>One can rectify the middle name on the ticket without modifying the surname.</li>\r\n	<li>Passenger can alter their nicknames to legal names on the Delta Airline ticket or boarding pass.</li>\r\n	<li>A traveler can carry out simple additions to a name without altering the whole name.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Name Change Correction Situations</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Unfortunately, there cannot be any one situation based on which a passenger applies for a change of name on the ticket. For example, some want to alter their last name, while some may like to change their middle name. Hence, you must know all these situations to proceed appropriately according to your purpose.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>1. Delta Airlines - Name Change After Marriage</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The name inconsistency arises due to marriage. It is a common problem among all women. After marriage, a woman&rsquo;s last name gets changed, which causes an issue during the flight boarding process. It is because their last name doesn&rsquo;t match their individual I&rsquo;d cards. However, they can produce some legal documents pertaining to their marriage. Further, a woman may apply for a&nbsp;<strong>change of surname on the ticket</strong> in the case of divorce.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. Delta Airlines - Middle Name Corrections</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Middle name is not a mandatory field to fill. But if you fill it, make sure you mention it correctly. It means your middle name should match the name written on your government identification card. On the initiation of the change procedure, the agent will perform the following steps to ensure the correction of the name:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Look into the PNR to correct the name.</li>\r\n	<li>Incorporate an OSI message to advise that the&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> is completed.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, the airline will issue a ticket in exchange. Further, you will not be able to make any more changes to flights and dates.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Delta Airlines - Last Name Additions and Corrections</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Before falling under any kind of complexion with the wrong name, make sure to avoid the differences in your name while comparing it with the name in the government ID. In case of modifying the surname, you should know the following few things:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Delta Airlines allows customers to add only three characters to their last names.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The name correction process will be the same as the middle name. However, the only change will be in the OSI notification.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Delta Airlines guests can add something to their last names without modifying the first name. For this, below are the essential guidelines:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you want to&nbsp;<strong>add a name</strong> to your surname, then the procedure will be similar to that of a middle name. After the correction, the traveler can check out the name in the PNR.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The guest will get a reissued ticket, and after its receipt, the guest cannot make any further rectifications.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>4. Delta Airlines - Last &amp; First Name Reversed</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It sometimes happens that a passenger mistakenly writes the last name in place of the first name on the flight ticket and vice versa. If you want to amend this mistake, it is essential to follow the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/name-change/delta-airlines-name-change-policy\" target=\"_self\"><strong>Delta Airlines Name Change</strong></a><strong> or Correction Policy</strong>. The reversed name change process is akin to the above correction procedures. Only the OSI message will be different.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If there are other reasons besides those mentioned above, a passenger can contact Delta Airlines directly.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Methods of Changing the Name on Delta Airlines Ticket</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have made an error in your name while booking your flight, don&rsquo;t worry because there are different ways of correcting them. Delta Airlines has specified three ways of&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on tickets</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following are the three ways in which a passenger can either change or correct their incorrect name on the ticket:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 1 - Name Change Through Delta Official Website</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the most common ways of rectifying the name on the Delta ticket is through the official website. To know how it processes, check out the following steps that you have to go along with:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Visit the formal <a href=\"https://www.delta.com/\" target=\"_blank\">website</a> of Delta Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>Fill in all the booking details and sign in to your account.</li>\r\n	<li>Tap on the &ldquo;Manage My Travel&rdquo; icon.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Enter your Delta ticket info and press the search button.</li>\r\n	<li>It will take you to your Delta Airline ticket, in which you will want to make a name change.</li>\r\n	<li>Click on the ticket and open it.</li>\r\n	<li>Tap on the icon placed on the upper right side of your screen, and you will see the &ldquo;Edit&rdquo; icon.</li>\r\n	<li>Press the Edit button.</li>\r\n	<li>Find the option to change your name.</li>\r\n	<li>Type the name and scroll down to save the changes.</li>\r\n	<li>Last, pay if needed.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Once these steps are performed, you will receive an email or notification from the airline confirming your name change on the Delta ticket.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 2 - Flight Name Change Via Phone Call</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Some travelers like to make rectifications through an official website, while others go for a more plausible mode to connect directly with officials. In this, the passenger contacts the airline&#39;s office through a phone call. The number given by the airline to connect with agents is {{PHONE_NUMBER}}.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once you reach the agent, he will ask for the necessary details regarding your reservation, including your PNR or e-ticket number. Further, the agent will ask you about the reason for the change and other relevant information. Upon receipt of all the details, the agent will proceed with the name change process. You can either stay on the call until the name change request is confirmed or ask for a confirmation email.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 3 - Name Change at Airport Kiosk</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Delta Airlines name correction policy offers name rectification at the airport Kiosk. With the help of the airport Kiosk, you can alter your name on the reservation through a simple self-service device. If you face any difficulty using this service, you can seek assistance from airport officials.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To change the name at the airport Kiosk, you can proceed with the following steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Open the gadget and log in to your account through the airline&rsquo;s official website.</li>\r\n	<li>Fill in your e-ticket number.</li>\r\n	<li>Open the trip details page and follow the directions to reach the change name option.</li>\r\n	<li>Rectify the name on the Delta ticket.</li>\r\n	<li>Last, take a print of your new boarding pass.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The airport Kiosk device is quite simple to use and saves passengers from the trouble of going through a long process.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Charges for Name Change Corrections</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Delta Airlines allows a passenger to rectify his name within 24 hours free of cost. It means the traveler will not have to pay any fee for name correction within the first twenty-four hours of booking their reservations. After 24 hours, the customer will have to pay a fee. The charges may vary from $75-$500.&nbsp;</p>', '931517.webp', '2022-10-14 05:00:28', '2022-10-31 18:22:58'),
(6, 10, NULL, 'United Airlines Name Change Policy', 'united-airlines-name-change-policy', 'United Airlines only allows those passengers on board whose names on the ticket and photo ID are the same. So, if you have accidentally written the wrong essentials of your name, you should know how to correct it before boarding the flight. If there are any name differences, you can rectify them according to United Airlines\' name change policy.', 'United Airlines Name Change and Correction Policy | Fee', 'United Airlines Name change policy allows the passenger to correct, add name and replace names on flight tickets. Follow the necessary steps for name correction.', 'United Airlines flying plane', '<p>United Airlines only allows those passengers on board whose names on the ticket and photo ID are the same. So, if you have accidentally written the wrong essentials of your name, you should know how to correct it before boarding the flight. If there are any name differences, you can rectify them according to United Airlines&#39; name change policy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before requesting a&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong>, you must know that United Airlines only allows minor changes in the name. It means a passenger cannot change the complete name or any part of the name on their United ticket.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A traveler has to abide by the following criteria to make corrections in their name:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The flight must be United Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of code-share and interline, United Airlines name correction requests will be honored on United&rsquo;s portion of the route.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The ticket inventory should start with the number 016.</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger is only allowed one reissue per ticket when doing a name correction on United&rsquo;s ticket.</li>\r\n	<li>If a customer is asking for additional changes in their United Airlines ticket, then those alterations will be considered as the name change. Thereby, such additions will be subject to the name change policy of United Airlines. As per that, there will be an increase in the ticket price.</li>\r\n	<li>As per United&rsquo;s name change policy, no modification can be done to the flight date, time, fare classes, and fare base code under any circumstances.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger can only be allowed to make minor alterations to the name, and that must match the government ID card.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>With the request for the&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>, a passenger cannot amend the date of birth and gender.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The customer&rsquo;s date of birth and name would be subject to United Airlines&rsquo; name change policy.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A traveler can make minor changes to the mistakes in the date of birth only when they are committed while making the reservation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>United Airlines&#39; name change allows one correction per reservation. If you want to make further changes, there will be additional charges to complete the formalities.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Types of United Airlines Name Correction Policy</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When a traveler commits an error while reserving a ticket with United Airlines, a name change policy allows them to eliminate this trouble. There are three categories under which a passenger can rectify the misspelled name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following are three types of name change policies under United Airlines:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Category 1 - Simple Modifications in a Name</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When the passenger&rsquo;s name is incorrect on the ticket, the standard procedure will be used to correct the name. According to the&nbsp;<strong>United Airlines name correction policy</strong>, simple mistakes on the reservation ticket don&rsquo;t require the burden of documentation. These alterations are limited to spelling errors or a few letter mistakes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Examples of simple name modifications are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Correcting a typo error in the spelling of the name. For instance, altering the first name Charli to Charlie and the last name Mathwe to Mathew.</li>\r\n	<li>Making a modification in the name on the reservation to or from a nickname. For example, Ally to AL.</li>\r\n	<li>Rectifying the prefix or title on the ticket. For example, Miss to Mrs, Mr. to Dr.</li>\r\n	<li>Modifying the middle name on the boarding pass. For instance, Elizabeth Richard Smith to Elizabeth R. Smith.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Category 2 - Significant Alterations in a Name</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Significant changes in the name are generally those alterations where a passenger has to submit legal documents supporting the modification. These changes are more substantial in comparison to the simple ones. Significant changes often happen in the event of marriage or divorce, where you must disclose documents supporting your request.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the documents that a passenger must show for a legal name change:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In the case of divorce, you must present the papers outlining the separation settlement.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the event of a marriage, you must show a legal document supporting the name change.</li>\r\n	<li>If you have changed your full name, you must show a government-issued document that includes your old and new information.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Category 3 - Affidavit with an Alternative Name</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It may happen that you don&rsquo;t have the legal documents to support your name change. In such a case, United Airlines name change policy allows a customer to alter the name by showing the affidavit with an alternative name. It means a passenger can&nbsp;<strong>replace the name on the ticket</strong> with the help of an affidavit. With the help of an affidavit, a traveler can also generate a photo ID copy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>How to Change the Name on the Ticket under the United Airlines Name Correction Policy?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Every passenger uses their convenience while applying for a change of name on the ticket. That is why United Airlines have provided many options for rectifying a name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As per United Airlines Name Correction Policy, you can alter a name in the following ways:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 1 - Name Change Via Affidavit</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger of United Airlines can request a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong> via affidavit. When you don&rsquo;t have legal documents to show to the concerned body, in that case, you must submit the affidavit. You must have a copy of an affidavit if you apply for a name change through this method. In addition to this, you have to email the notarized documents to the address mentioned below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Center of Service for MileagePlus, Postal Code 1394, 77251-1394 Houston, TX</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 2 - Rectify Name Via Phone Call</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes, a passenger wants to modify the name on an urgent basis. In such cases, the facility of calling the officials is the most suitable method. An agent can facilitate the <a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/name-change/united-airlines-name-change-policy\">United Airlines&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong></a> via call. When you dial the client service number, a representative will answer the call and take your request further.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The representative will collect your personal information. Therefore, they will apply the necessary changes to your name according to the information provided by you and the name change policy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to accelerate the process of the name change, call us now at ____</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Method 3 - Alter Name Via Airport Visit</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>When you want to take in-person assistance for changing your name, it is best to visit the airport. The United Airlines representative will help you in solving your issue. You can tell them the problem you are facing while changing your name. If the airline supports the provision to alter your name change, you will get informed regarding the same.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Further, the representative will tell you about the name change process according to the United Airlines name correction policy. Hence, you can follow the procedure and change your name.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>United Airlines Name Change Charges</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger can&nbsp;<strong>replace the name on the ticket</strong> subject to some charge. The fee for a name change can depend upon the time of the request. If you modify the name within 24 hours of booking, you shall be charged $75.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any modification made after 24 hours and two hours before <a href=\"https://www.united.com/ual/en/us/fly/contact/mileageplus/name-change.html\" target=\"_blank\">the</a> arranged departure will cost a customer $200, alongside the difference in fare.</p>', '480948.webp', '2022-10-14 06:41:38', '2022-10-31 18:23:44');
