(7, 11, NULL, 'United Airlines Cancellation Policy', 'united-airlines-cancellation-policy', 'A passenger always worries when it comes to canceling a flight. The reasons for flight cancellation can vary from person to person. But the hassle travelers faces during cancellation is primarily chaotic. However, it is not the case with United Airlines.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>A passenger always worries when it comes to canceling a flight. The reasons for flight cancellation can vary from person to person. But the hassle travelers faces during cancellation is primarily chaotic. However, it is not the case with United Airlines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/cancellation-policy/united-airlines-cancellation-policy\" target=\"_self\"><strong>United Airlines cancellation policy</strong></a> is flexible and helps a passenger to cancel the flight without hassle. Let&rsquo;s understand how this airline&#39;s cancellation policy is helpful for you while canceling flights.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines Flight Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As per United&rsquo;s cancellation policy, a traveler can request flight cancelation 3 hours before the scheduled departure for international flights. Similarly, in the case of domestic flights, a passenger can cancel the flight before 2 hours.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You should know about the following other flight-related cancellation policies:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The flight cancellation request is subject to some fees. The amount may vary depending on the trip type, fare rule associated with the reservation, and cabin class.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>As per the&nbsp;<strong>flight cancellation policy</strong>, economy reservations are non-refundable and non-changeable after 24 hours of purchase.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If a passenger is marked a no-show for a flight, the value of the reservation may be forfeited.</li>\r\n	<li>If United Airlines has canceled the flight, the traveler would not need to pay any cancellation fee. Besides, if you deny taking the alternative flight, you will get a refund on the unused portion of the ticket.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the event of the death of a traveler, immediate family member, or traveling companion, united will waive the cancellation fee. In that case, you will get a refund amount on the unflown flight segment.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines Covid Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the&nbsp;<strong>flight cancellation policy</strong>, a passenger has to take note of the following travel requirement and restrictions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Your flight may get canceled if the government or local public health department has ordered you to quarantine.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If you have been denied boarding on international flights, you cannot rebook.</li>\r\n	<li>A medical statement declaring that you don&rsquo;t have Covid-19 is a must for traveling.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>As per the United policy, a vaccination certificate for international travel is mandatory.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger with Covid symptoms will not be allowed to board the flight.</li>\r\n	<li>The traveler with health issues or covid related symptoms will require to submit a health declaration, medical certificate, or a doctor&rsquo;s note.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Flyers may not be allowed to board if they are not wearing a mask or covering their face while traveling to or from United Airlines.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines 24-Hour Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You can get a full refund with no fees if you&nbsp;<strong>cancel the ticket</strong> within 24 hours of booking the flight. However, some banks or credit card companies may temporarily hold your funds on your card. In such a case, contact the bank to understand their policies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Following are the terms and conditions of&nbsp;<strong>United Airlines 24 hours cancellation</strong> policy:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The 24-hour applies from the time you have reserved the flight.</li>\r\n	<li>All the refund amount will go to your original form of payment except for the booking made with a United gift certificate.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>United&rsquo;s 24-hour policy is applicable on all basic economy fares unless you cancel within the timeframe.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If you cancel after 24 hours, then a fee of $200 will apply to you.</li>\r\n	<li>The 24 hours will begin from the moment your ticket number generates.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If your PNR consists of more than nine members, the 24-hour&nbsp;<strong>cancellation policy&nbsp;</strong>will not be applicable.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The tickets purchased with e-certificates are not eligible under United&rsquo;s 24-hour policy.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The bookings held but not yet purchased are not eligible under this cancellation policy.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Cancel United Airlines Reservation?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Under United&#39;s cancelation policy, a passenger gets various modes of canceling a United flight ticket. You can use any of these methods to cancel the flight at your convenience. Now, let&rsquo;s go through the following ways to call off the flight ticket:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Cancel the Ticket Via Website Online</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A customer can cancel a united airlines ticket online with the help of a website. For ticket cancelation, you need to follow a few steps. You can cancel the ticket by following the below-mentioned steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Go to the <a href=\"https://www.united.com/\">website</a> of United Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>Find the My Trips tab.</li>\r\n	<li>Submit the booking reference number and the passenger&rsquo;s last name.</li>\r\n	<li>Choose the flight segment that you would like to cancel.</li>\r\n	<li>After selecting the segment, pay the necessary fees to complete the request.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, you will get a confirmation mail on your email ID.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Cancel the Ticket Via Phone Number</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to cancel the flight ticket due to an unforeseen circumstance, you can reach out to a United Airlines executive via call. Under this method, you can dial the customer service number and connect with the agent. Once you connect with the executive, you can request them to cancel your ticket. Then, they will ask you to provide the ticket number or booking confirmation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After the necessary details, they will ask you to pay the cancellation fee and any other charges over the phone. Later, the agent will cancel your ticket and confirm the same in the email.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Cancel Flight by Visiting Airport</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Canceling a flight by visiting the airport is an offline method. In this, you can go to the departure airport and request flight cancellation up to 3 hours before the departure time. If you have checked in for the flight, you must cancel the check-in first to claim the refund on your booking. It is one of the most feasible methods to cancel the flight offline.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are confused about the cancellation process and don&rsquo;t know how to do it, we are here to help. Contact us at {{PHONE_NUMBER}}.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines Policy on Cancelled Flights</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A flight is not only called off by the passenger but also by the airline. Although United Airlines works hard to take care of its customers and bring them to their destinations, it sometimes fails. Usually, it happens due to unpredicted circumstances. In that case, United Airlines do its best to assist travelers in the best possible way.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some types of canceled flights under the United Airlines flight&nbsp;<strong>cancellation policy</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Delayed Flights</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have booked your ticket with United Airlines, they will notify you via email or text message on your number. You will get a new departure time. With the United Airlines app, you can get up-to-date flight details. You can also check the website for flight status updates or real-time updates.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If your flight gets delayed for more than three hours, the airline will provide you with an alternate flight and a service voucher for a meal.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Missed Connecting Flights</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes, a passenger may miss a connecting flight. It may happen when you assume that you have a single flight for all the routes. However, it can also happen when your existing flight is held back, because of which you miss your subsequent flight. In such cases, the airline will ensure that the passengers arrive at their final destination.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s what will happen if you miss a United Airlines flight:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>United Airlines will reroute your flight. It may take some time due to the lack of alternative flights.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Airlines will constantly update you about any modifications to your connecting flights.</li>\r\n	<li>If your reservation includes a flight from another airline, it will require a separate ticket. In this case, you will need to contact the issuing agency to make modifications.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Cancelled Flights</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Often, flights get canceled due to unforeseen circumstances. The reasons for&nbsp;<strong>booking cancellations</strong> can be bad weather, technical problems, or others. In the event of flight cancellation, United Airlines will contact you via message or email.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the case of ticket cancellation, a passenger gets the following three choices:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A customer can modify the travel date to 7 days in either direction. In this case, no additional cost will be applicable.</li>\r\n	<li>Under the United Airlines cancellation policy, the airline will reroute your ticket to the final destination. It is necessary to know that rerouting may take some time.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If you don&rsquo;t want an alternate flight, you can claim a refund for the unused portion of the booking.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. Overbooked Flights</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At times, the airlines accept more reservations than the usual capacity of aircraft to accommodate people. It is because not every passenger board the flight.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If something like this occurs, the following things will happen:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The airlines will transfer you to a different flight.</li>\r\n	<li>According to the&nbsp;<strong>United Airlines cancellation policy</strong>, the airline will assist you with a new booking and compensation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>United Airlines will accommodate you with the new alternative flight to your destination. Also, they will compensate you for delays and inconveniences.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines Ticket Cancellation Compensation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger will be entitled to compensation if the flight has been canceled, delayed, or denied boarding. Under the cancellation policy, the compensation depends on several factors like length of delay, cause, and flight destination.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The compensation for delayed flights will be:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th><strong>New Flight Arrival Time</strong></th>\r\n			<th><strong>Compensation(% of Ticket fare)</strong></th>\r\n			<th><strong>Maximum Payout (USD)</strong></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Within one hour of original arrival time</td>\r\n			<td>None</td>\r\n			<td>None</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Between 1-3 hours after original arrival time</td>\r\n			<td>200%</td>\r\n			<td>$675</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>More than 3 hours after original arrival time</td>\r\n			<td>400%</td>\r\n			<td>$1350</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>In the case of denied boarding, the airline will offer the following compensation:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th><strong>Flight Distance</strong></th>\r\n			<th><strong>Maximum Compensation (USD)</strong></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Below 1500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>150</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Between 1500 Km and 3500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>200</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>More than 3500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>300</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>As per the&nbsp;<strong>United Airlines flight cancellation policy,</strong> if your flight gets canceled, you will get the following compensation:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th><strong>Flight Distance</strong></th>\r\n			<th><strong>Maximum Compensation (USD)</strong></th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Below 1500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>300</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Between 1500 Km and 3500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>400</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>More than 3500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>600</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines Refund Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>United Airlines cancellation policy allows refund requests for only unused/unflown portions of the ticket. For this, there are several guidelines that a passenger should consider before requesting a refund for a reservation:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger who purchased a ticket one week before and canceled it within 24 hours of purchase will be eligible for a refund. In addition, no cancellation fee will be applicable.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Basic Economy tickets cannot be refunded if canceled after 24 hours. That means you will get a refund only if you have canceled it within 24 hours of purchase.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>According to the&nbsp;<strong>United flight cancellation policy</strong>, the fee will depend on the fare rules of your ticket.</li>\r\n	<li>A person may not qualify for a voluntary refund for non-refundable fares, but the ticket&rsquo;s fare value will get converted into a Future Flight Credit.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Generally, flight tickets have 12-month viability from the day of issue. However, the tickets purchased on or before December 31, 2022, have validity up to December 31, 2022. It means your travel must not begin after December 31, 2022, and must complete within a year from the outbound travel date.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The refund amount depends on several factors. For example, the refund for partially used tickets will be calculated on a prorated basis. Other tax and&nbsp;<strong>cancellation fee</strong>s will be applicable as per the rules.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger who purchased the air ticket by credit card will get the refund within 7 days. On the other hand, all other passengers will get the cancellation refund within 20 business days.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The customer will get the refund back to the original form of payment.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>United Airlines Cancellation Fee</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>United Airlines will not charge any cancellation fee if it happens due to covid-19 restrictions. Other than that, a passenger will have to pay a cancellation fee. As per&nbsp;<strong>United Airlines cancellation policy</strong>, a customer with a basic economy ticket will not have to pay any cancellation fee.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the passenger has non-refundable and&nbsp;<strong>refundable airline tickets</strong>, the fee will be $200 for domestic and $400 for international flights. With United Airlines, you will get ease in handling the cancellation process.&nbsp;</p>', '517608.jpg', '2022-10-20 16:44:26', '2022-10-31 18:24:48'),
(8, 11, NULL, 'Alaska Airlines Cancellation Policy', 'alaska-airlines-cancellation-policy', 'No matter how excited you are about your trip, there is always scope for fickle moments when you may have to cancel your flight. In such unfortunate circumstances, if the cancellation process is also confusing, it may add to your frustration even more. However, the Alaska Airlines cancellation policy is easy to understand and saves time & money.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>If you want to cancel the flight, you need to take the help of the cancellation policy. There are guidelines that you must follow so that you can cancel the ticket and get the correct refund. Let&rsquo;s look at the cancellation policy of Alaska Airlines.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Flight Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger cancels an air ticket for many reasons. Following are some of the main reasons for flight cancellations:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A customer can cancel the flight due to any mishappening.</li>\r\n	<li>In case of some illness, a traveler cancels the travel plan.</li>\r\n	<li>If the flight schedule changes, the passenger cancels the ticket.</li>\r\n	<li>Sometimes, the reason can be a loss of a loved one, due to which the passenger cancels the flight.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want that your ticket canceled correctly and you get the correct refund, you must adhere to the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/cancellation-policy/alaska-airlines-cancellation-policy\"><strong>Alaska Airlines cancellation policy</strong></a> guideline. A passenger must consider following rules and regulations while canceling the air ticket:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If the ticket has been purchased more than 24 hours before the scheduled departure, the flight can be canceled within 24 hours of reservation for a full refund.</li>\r\n	<li>The main cabin and first-class ticket prices can be changed within 24 hours of booking with no change fee if the tickets are purchased more than 24 hours prior to scheduled departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If the saver fares are purchased at least 24 hours before the scheduled departure, the passenger cannot change them. However, they can be canceled and rebooked within 24 hours of booking.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of a refundable ticket, a passenger can request a refund in the original form of payment online.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You can cancel or change your ticket until the time of departure except for saver fares.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of a non-refundable ticket, a customer will get a credit for a future flight.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If changes are made during the check-in window, you will pay a fee ranging from $25-$50. There will be no fee if you have MVP Gold status with the airline.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You can get your Mileage Plan miles back in your account if you inform the airline about cancelation or change before departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines 24-Hour Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>After getting an insight into the standard cancellation policy, you must also learn about the 24-hour cancellation policy. This policy will help you know the benefits of canceling the ticket within 24 hours. The policy applies to every ticket type, including Saver fares.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As per&nbsp;<strong>Alaska Airlines 24-hour cancellation policy</strong>, a passenger can cancel a ticket within 24 hours of purchase and get a full refund. However, if you cancel the ticket after 24 hours of reservation, you will pay a cancellation fee.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It will apply to tickets whose departure times are more than 24 hours from the time of reservation. You can cancel the ticket within 24 hours of departure, but you will pay a cancellation fee.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Cancellation Policy for Covid-19</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The covid pandemic has affected airlines and their passengers in numerous ways. Due to this, the airline or passengers may cancel the ticket for safety reasons. Under&nbsp;<strong>Alaska Airlines cancellation policy</strong>, the Peace of Mind Waivers will apply to flight bookings between February 27, 2020, and April 30, 2021.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As per this, a passenger will not have to pay a fee for ticket cancellation. As of now, no charges are being levied on passengers for canceling flight tickets after May 1, 2021. Until further notice, a passenger will not pay any fee if the reason for cancellation is Covid-19 and its restrictions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Cancel Alaska Airlines Flight?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alaska cancellation policy provides different ways for customers to&nbsp;<strong>cancel reservations</strong>. A traveler cancels a flight ticket at their convenience with the help of the following methods:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 1 - Cancellation Through the Official Website</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Alaska Airlines assists a passenger with flight cancellations through the website. It is one of the easy ways to cancel a ticket. Here are the steps you can follow to use this method for ticket cancellation:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First, go to the browser and open the Alaska Airlines <a href=\"https://www.alaskaair.com/\">website</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>Second, log in to your account and fill in all the information.</li>\r\n	<li>Third, navigate the My Trip tab.</li>\r\n	<li>Fourth, select the Alaska flight booking that you want to cancel.</li>\r\n	<li>Fifth, tap on the Confirm tab to move with the cancellation.</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, you will get an email confirmation after the successful cancellation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Once the process ends, wait for an email confirmation. If you don&rsquo;t receive the email within the mentioned period, you need to contact customer care.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 2 - Cancellation Through Toll-Free Number</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger can&nbsp;<strong>cancel a reservation</strong> by contacting the airline directly. With direct assistance from airport personnel, the passenger can cancel the ticket anytime. You can connect with the airline at any hour of the day.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the steps to cancel the Alaska ticket on call:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Call on the Alaska Airlines toll-free number.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>A customer service representative will ask you about the ticket details.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>After gathering all the details, the agent will process the cancellation request.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You can ask about the cancellation fee and&nbsp;<strong>ticket refund</strong> amount if you have any doubts about the same.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Calling Alaska Airlines toll-free number({{PHONE_NUMBER}}) to cancel the air ticket is one of the easiest ways.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 3 - Cancellation Through Live Chat</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Live Chat is another convenient way to cancel an Alaska flight ticket without hassle. For this method, a customer must be ready with ticket details. This method assists travelers with an effortless cancellation process. A passenger can use the Live Chat with the help of the following steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To use this method, open the &ldquo;Contact Us&rdquo; page on the Alaska Airlines website.</li>\r\n	<li>Find the &ldquo;Start Chat&rdquo; option and begin the conversation by introducing your name and other details.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You will connect with the chatbot. Then, the chatbot will ask for more details, like the booking code.</li>\r\n	<li>After providing the necessary information, wait for the&nbsp;<strong>booking cancellation</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>During this method, you may have to wait a few minutes while details get fetched into the system for processing ticket cancellation. Because without the details, the request may get canceled.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are confused about how to&nbsp;<strong>cancel a reservation</strong>, contact us at {{PHONE_NUMBER}}. We will help you get it done in minimum time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Compensation Terms</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes, flights get canceled or delayed due to unforeseen reasons. In such cases, the passengers face trouble. To reduce their difficulties, the airline compensates the travelers. For this, the airline pays an amount to passengers. But Alaska Airlines don&rsquo;t pay compensation in every situation. So, you need to understand when you will get compensation and when not.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As per&nbsp;<strong>Alaska Airlines cancellation policy</strong>, a passenger must be aware of the following compensation terms:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In the case of Alaska Airlines last-minute cancellation, a European passenger will get compensation if the flight also connects European airports. If the flight has been canceled less than two weeks before the departure, European passengers will get the compensation.</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger will not get any compensation if the airline is providing an alternative flight.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The amount of compensation can go up to $700 per person.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In other cases, the compensation varies for both canceled and delayed flights. Here is the compensation amount a passenger receives in the case of canceled and delayed flights:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Compensation When the Flights Get Canceled by Alaska Airlines</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As per the&nbsp;<strong>Alaska cancellation policy</strong>, a person with a refundable ticket will get compensation for the fare. The passenger will get the compensation on the same payment mode from which they purchased the ticket. In the case of the non-refundable ticket, the customer will get compensation in Alaska Airline&rsquo;s wallet.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A traveler receives credits and rewards if the flight gets canceled due to Covid-19 restrictions. However, a passenger can demand a&nbsp;<strong>ticket refund</strong> instead of reward points.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger will get the following compensation in case of flights canceled by Alaska Airlines:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Distance</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Types of Flight</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Amount of Refund(Per Person)</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Less than 1500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>All Flights</td>\r\n			<td>Up to&nbsp;&euro;250</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>More than 1500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>Internal EU flights</td>\r\n			<td>Up to&nbsp;&euro;400</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Between 1500-3500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>Non-internal EU flights</td>\r\n			<td>Up to&nbsp;&euro;400</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Over 3500 Km</td>\r\n			<td>Non-internal flights of EU</td>\r\n			<td>Up to&nbsp;&euro;600</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Compensation When the Flights Get Delayed by Alaska Airlines</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Alaska&#39;s flight cancellation</strong> policy also focuses on delays. Delays only occur in certain situations. But due to these delays, a customer faces issues with their travel plan. Here are the following terms and conditions for such cancellations:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If the flight is delayed for 3 hours or more, a passenger will get compensation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The European passengers will also get compensation if the Alaska flight was scheduled to travel via European Airport.</li>\r\n	<li>The compensation amount can be up to $700 per person in the case of delayed flights.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Refund Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The refund policy is a vital aspect of the&nbsp;<strong>Alaska cancellation policy</strong>. If you cancel an Alaska flight, you can apply for a refund. For that, you must be aware of the refund policy. The ticket refund policy varies according to different circumstances. If the passenger cancels the flight within the correct time frame, the refund will get initiated in 5-8 business days.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A person gets a refund on cancellation only if the request meets the following eligibility conditions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger can only initiate a refund request on a ticket purchased directly from Alaska Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>A saver ticket owner may have fewer chances to get a refund. It is because they are at discounted rates.</li>\r\n	<li>The refundable ticket holder will get a complete refund.</li>\r\n	<li>The ticket purchased from the middleman or agency will not be eligible for a refund.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Alaska Airlines Cancellation Fee</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you cancel your reservation, you may or may not pay the cancellation fee. A passenger will not have to pay any charges in case of cancellation within 24 hours from the booking time. The fee will be waived, and the travelers will get a full refund.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A customer will pay the&nbsp;<strong>Alaska Airlines cancellation fee</strong> in the following scenarios:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger will pay a standard amount if the ticket has been canceled within 24 hours of the departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The fee can apply to all fares, classes, and trips.</li>\r\n	<li>A customer may pay nearly $125 for all domestic flights cancellation or changes.</li>\r\n	<li>For international flights cancellation, a passenger may pay between $200 to $500.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', '224774.webp', '2022-10-27 20:28:01', '2022-10-31 18:25:42'),
(9, 11, NULL, 'Delta Airlines Cancellation Policy', 'delta-airlines-cancellation-policy', 'Canceling a flight has been a hassling task. You go through long and puzzling processes. However, Delta Airlines cancellation policy is flexible and customer-friendly. In every situation, a passenger can effortlessly cancel a ticket in different ways. So, letâs understand how you can cancel your Delta Airlines flight tickets.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h2>Delta Airlines Cancellation Policy Rules</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger must know the rules for requesting Delta ticket cancellation. There are different rule considerations that a customer must understand. You must consider the following conditions for ticket cancellation:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Refundable Ticket Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have purchased a refundable ticket, you must consider the following points:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger can claim a refund on Delta refundable tickets if the ticket gets canceled three hours before the scheduled departure. Similarly, the main cabin fares can be dropped at the last minute and canceled up to two hours before scheduled departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>According to the&nbsp;<strong>Delta Airlines cancellation policy</strong>, any refundable ticket clubbed with hotels, car rental, or a combination of them would get refunded only on airfare. Refunds for hotel or car rental can only be claimed with a third party and will not be covered under the Delta Airlines policy.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In case of a no-show, a passenger has to pay a no-show penalty of $150 and a cancellation fee of $200. After payment of the necessary amount, the passenger will get a refund on the rest of the fare value.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Non-Refundable Ticket Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are the key points you must understand before claiming the refund on the non-refundable ticket under the Delta&nbsp;<strong>Airline cancellations</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A passenger is eligible for a refund if the reservation gets canceled within 24 hours from the time of booking. In addition, the date of departure must be seven days or more from the time of cancellation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>As per&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/cancellation-policy/delta-airlines-cancellation-policy\"><strong>Delta Airlines cancellation policy</strong></a>, non-refundable tickets are not eligible for extra legroom seats or an upgrade on the service.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Non-refundable Delta fare is eligible for a refund only if the flight gets delayed, canceled, or attributed to the airline directly.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Covid Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger must follow the Delta Covid policy rules to travel with Delta Airlines:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Delta refund will not be allowed if you have canceled the flight 4 hours before the departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In case you have initiated Delta flight cancellation within four hours of departure time, a refund will not be allowed.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If Delta has canceled the flight or initiated flight suspension, the passenger will get a full refund on the fare value. The passenger will not be entitled to pay the&nbsp;<strong>Delta Cancellation fee</strong>. Delta refund will be applicable if the flight gets delayed for three or more hours.</li>\r\n	<li>If the passenger has initiated the flight rescheduled three days before the departure, they will get a free reschedule. There will be no penalty, and a fare difference will be applicable.</li>\r\n	<li>Delta Airlines will apply a cancellation fee and penalty for the rescheduled flight between 72 hours and 4 hours before the scheduled departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta 24-Hour Cancellation Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger can cancel a reservation within 24 hours from the booking date if the following conditions are satisfied:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>At the time of cancellation, if the departure is later than seven or more days, the passenger can cancel the reservation within 24 hours.</li>\r\n	<li>Delta Airlines 24-hour cancellation will be applicable on all types of fares, irrespective of the class of service.</li>\r\n	<li>The Skymiles tickets will not be applicable for the 24-hour cancellation policy.</li>\r\n	<li>A group booking of more than nine members will not be applicable for 24-hour cancellation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Delta&#39;s 24-hour&nbsp;<strong>cancellation policy</strong> will apply to all flights originating to and from the US and Canada.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The rescheduled and redeemed flights will not cover under this policy.</li>\r\n	<li>The tickets purchased using e-certificates are exempted from the 24-hour cancellation policy.</li>\r\n	<li>Delta refund request will process within 7-10 days to the original form of payment. If the flight booking has been purchased with Delta gift certificates, the amount will get credited to the electronic travel certificates.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Cancel Delta Airlines Flight Ticket?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Delta Airlines offers three methods for&nbsp;<strong>booking cancellation</strong>. Passengers can use the following modes to cancel a flight at their convenience:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 1 - Delta Airlines Flight Cancellation Online</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Flight cancellation through online mode is one of the easiest ways. Follow these steps to initiate Delta flight cancellation online:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Visit Delta Airlines official <a href=\"https://www.delta.com/\">website</a> and reach to My Trip Section.</li>\r\n	<li>To retrieve the booking, enter the confirmation code with the first and last name of the passenger.</li>\r\n	<li>Pick the flight that you want to cancel.</li>\r\n	<li>You will pay a fee to initiate the cancellation request.</li>\r\n	<li>You will receive the refund in the original payment method or Delta Airlines flight credit, depending on the ticket type.</li>\r\n	<li>The refund will be credited in the original form of payment in 7-10 business days.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 2 - Delta Flight Cancellation Over the Phone</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If the online method is not convenient for you, try calling Delta Airlines for reaching to executives. With this method, you can call the airline and take the help of an executive to cancel the flight. The following steps will facilitate canceling your Delta flight:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>While contacting Delta Airlines, keep your flight confirmation number handy.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Tell the Delta executive about the flight segment you want to cancel.</li>\r\n	<li>According to the Delta Airlines&nbsp;<strong>cancellation policy</strong>, passengers can claim a refund or credit on their ticket.</li>\r\n	<li>In case of restricted fares, you will get a Delta Cancellation travel credit. In addition, you will get a travel voucher on your registered mail id. The tickets purchased can be valid for one year from the date of purchase.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 3 - Delta Flight Cancellation at the Airport</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If the above two methods are unsuitable, you can use this&nbsp;<strong>airline cancellations</strong> method. A passenger can cancel a ticket likely up to three hours before the scheduled departure. All you need to do is to go along with the following steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You need to visit the departure Airport and head straight to the Delta ticket counter.</li>\r\n	<li>Submit your confirmation code/PNR to the Delta executive.</li>\r\n	<li>Tell them about the segment you want to cancel.</li>\r\n	<li>The agent will ask you to pay a cancellation fee if any.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>You will get the refund or flight credit in the original payment method.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In the case of non-restricted or refundable tickets, the amount will get credited to the original payment method in 7-10 days.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Although these methods are easy to use, if you are still confused about the cancellation process, you can contact us at {{PHONE_NUMBER}}.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Airlines Cancellation Policy on Canceled Flights</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Due to unseen reasons, Delta Airlines sometimes cancel, delay, or deny boarding. In such situations, a traveler faces difficulties. To reduce their trouble, the airline compensates the customer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the situations when a passenger may struggle to board the flight:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delayed Delta Flight</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>According to&nbsp;<strong>Delta Airlines cancellation policy</strong>, it has certain responsibilities toward the passengers when the flight gets delayed due to unforeseen reasons. The obligations include assistance, rescheduling, refunds, and compensation of up to $1000. A passenger will be entitled to compensation or a refund if:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Delta flights get delayed for two or more hours. The passenger will get free-of-cost meals and refreshments.</li>\r\n	<li>If the flight gets delayed for six or more hours, the airline may reschedule the trip. If passengers deny the rescheduled flight, they can get a full refund.</li>\r\n	<li>Available flight is scheduled for the next day. In such cases, passengers are allowed for an overnight stay.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Canceled Delta Flight</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Flight cancellations by the airline are a rare yet significant phenomenon. It can affect passengers in numerous ways. An airline must inform its passengers about the involuntary cancellation at least two weeks before the departure.&nbsp; Delta offers an alternative flight or refund to the customer if the flight gets canceled due to bad weather conditions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you have been informed of cancellation within 14 days of departure, you can claim the refund on the unused portion of the reservation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>In case you have missed the connecting flight due to Delta canceled flight, you will get an alternative flight or refund on the unused portion.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Denied Delta Flight Boarding</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes, a passenger may be denied boarding because of overbooking of seats. In such cases, a traveler faces inconvenience. The following points have been specified under the&nbsp;<strong>cancellation policy</strong> to rule out their disruptions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If you have offered an alternate flight within one hour of the original departure time, you will not be entitled to flight cancellation compensation.</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger will get compensation of up to 200% of the original ticket price if Delta Airlines fails to provide an alternate flight.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Airlines Flight Cancellation Compensation</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the&nbsp;<strong>Delta cancellation policy</strong>, you will get flight cancellation compensation of up to $750:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If the Delta flight gets delayed for three hours or more.</li>\r\n	<li>A passenger will get the said compensation if the airline has informed of flight cancellation and delay within 14 days before the departure.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If the traveler has been denied boarding due to overbooking.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>As per the compensation policy, the amount may vary between $250 and $750 depending on the flight delay length:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Flight Distance</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Maximum Compensation(USD)</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Less than 2000 Km</td>\r\n			<td>250</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Between 2000 Km and 4000 Km</td>\r\n			<td>500</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>More than 4000 Km</td>\r\n			<td>750</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Airlines Refund Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger must know about the refund policy before canceling the booking. Here&rsquo;s the complete rundown of the Delta Airlines ticket cancellation refund policy:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>24-hour Cancellation</strong> - Under the Delta Airlines 24-hour cancellation policy, the passenger will get the full refund and will qualify for a waiver of a cancellation fee if:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The ticket is purchased in the last 24 hours, and</li>\r\n	<li>Date of departure is one week or more at the time of cancellation.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Free Cancellation</strong> - Basic Economy tickets are not eligible for flight changes. However, they are eligible for Delta flight cancellation within 24 hours of booking. If you don&rsquo;t cancel within 24 hours of purchase, you will not be allowed to get a refund unless you fall under the Covid-19 travel waiver.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Refundable Ticket Cancellation</strong> - A passenger must cancel their refundable ticket before initiating a Delta refund request. The ticket should be purchased through cash, credit card, or cheque.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Non-refundable Ticket Cancellation</strong> - A customer having a non-refundable ticket will not be eligible for a refund. However, you may be eligible to get e-credit against the ticket value after paying the cancellation fee of $200-$500. The cancellation fee will not be applicable if your flight originates within the United States. You can use the e-credit for any Delta flight.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Delta Airlines Refund Status</strong> - In case of the reservation is purchased with a&nbsp; credit card, the&nbsp;<strong>ticket refund</strong> will process within seven business days. On the other hand, the refund for bookings made with other payment methods will process within 20 business days of the request.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>Delta Airlines Cancellation Fees</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A passenger pays the cancellation fees for canceling a Delta Airlines reservation due to some reason. The cancellation fee is assessed based on per passenger per booking and is applicable on Delta flights only. Below are the key highlights that a passenger must know before requesting a cancellation:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Delta cancellation fee</strong> will be applicable on refundable and non-refundable fares, regardless of the class of service.</li>\r\n	<li>If the flight is booked with SkyMiles, the delta cancellation fee will not be applicable.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s the rundown of Delta Airlines cancellation fees:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Time</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Basic Economy</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Non-refundable Tickets</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Refundable Tickets</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>During the 24-hour cancellation period</td>\r\n			<td>Free of Charge+Fare difference</td>\r\n			<td>Free of Charge+Fare difference</td>\r\n			<td>Free of Charge+Fare difference</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>After 24-hour cancellation period</td>\r\n			<td>Not Allowed</td>\r\n			<td>$200+Fare difference</td>\r\n			<td>$200+Fare difference</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Within 24 hours of departure</td>\r\n			<td>Not Allowed</td>\r\n			<td>$300+Fare difference</td>\r\n			<td>$300+Fare difference</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', '753739.webp', '2022-10-27 20:31:01', '2022-10-31 18:26:26');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `cate_id`, `user_id`, `name`, `slug`, `short_desc`, `meta_title`, `meta_desc`, `image_alt`, `long_desc`, `post_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11, 10, NULL, 'Spirit Airlines Name Change Policy', 'spirit-airlines-name-change-policy', 'Travelers make mistakes in the spelling of their names while booking airlines. To correct those errors, a passenger must make modifications to their reservation. Every airline allows its customers to alter the incorrect name under the name change policy guidelines. Similarly, Spirit Airlines provides the chance to correct the misspelled name on the ticket.', 'Spirit Airlines Name Change Policy | Spirit Flight Name Correction', 'Spirit Airlines name change policy allows passengers to Change/Correct the wrong name on ticket online. Contact us and get all the information relating to name corrections.', NULL, '<p>A passenger is subject to following defined rules and policies to apply for&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong>. You can modify the first, last, and middle names by following the specified conditions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Spirit Airlines Name Correction Rules</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Spirit Airlines doesn&rsquo;t allow its passengers to fly with the incorrect name. So, before boarding the flight, you must ensure that you are traveling with the correct name on the reservation. If there are issues with your name, you can use the name change policy of Spirit Airlines to make necessary rectifications.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before requesting modification, you must understand the following rules of the name change policy of Spirit Airlines:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> is applied to the whole journey and not to a part of it.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The name change policy only allows minor corrections in the ticket.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Submitting certain legal documents is mandatory when you request any change in the particulars.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Spirit Airlines allows change in a maximum of 3 letters of first, last, and middle names.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The name change request will be permitted in the case of a legal change.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The modifications in details like birthdate, contact, sex, and passport details are allowed only with the production of government-verified documents.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The name on the ticket should be the same as in the government documents. So, if there is any suffix or prefix in your name in the government Id, you should also include it on your flight ticket.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If a passenger has booked with the segment of multiple flights, then the name change request must only be made for the Spirit Airlines segment.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The starting number of Spirit Airlines ticket inventory must be 095.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Types of Name Change Under Spirit Airlines Correction Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong> policy of Spirit Airlines incorporates different kinds of modifications, such as spelling errors and legal name changes. The two significant types of name changes are given below:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Modifications Due to Spelling Error</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If passengers have to make minor alterations to the ticket name, they can do it with the help of <a href=\"https://www.flyingrules.com/name-change/spirit-airlines-name-change-policy\">Spirit Airlines name change policy</a>. The minor error may have arisen due to a spelling mistake in the ticket. As long as the error is small, a passenger can correct it conveniently through the name change policy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to make any corrections to the name, you must contact the airline at least seven days before the scheduled departure. Also, the corrected name must match the credentials written on the government-issued ID/Passport.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Alterations Due to Legal Reasons</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the reservation</strong> can also be allowed for passengers who have legal reasons to change their name. The cause of their name change can be divorce, marriage, court cases, etc. In this kind of name change, a passenger must have to submit supporting documents for the change.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As approved by the court, a complete name change can be possible on Spirit Airlines flight tickets due to legal reasons.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Change Name on Spirit Airlines Flight Ticket?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Every customer has different requirements. According to that, they use several methods for a name change. Therefore, Spirit Airlines provides multiple approaches to a passenger to change the name on their ticket.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A traveler uses the following methods under Spirit Airlines name change policy:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 1 - Name Change Using Website</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Spirit Airlines website allows passengers to submit a complaint for a name change. In this complaint, you can specify the corrections that you want to make. The website may ask you to submit a few documents in support of the request. As soon as the airline receives your complaint, it will start working on it. You can submit your name change request by following the successive steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Visit the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.spirit.com/\" target=\"_blank\">website</a> of Spirit Airlines.</li>\r\n	<li>Next, click on the &ldquo;Manage My Travel&rdquo; option at the top of the home page. This option will help you to proceed with Spirit Airlines name change procedure.</li>\r\n	<li>Third, you must fill in the name mentioned in the passport and the flight reservation number.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Fourth, click on the &ldquo;Edit Booking&rdquo; option under the &ldquo;Upcoming Trips&rdquo; tab.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Fifth, you will enter the correct name under the name change option.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Sixth, the corrections relating to Spirit Airlines&nbsp;<strong>name change on the ticket</strong> will get updated on the site.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Lastly, you will see the correct details after refreshing the page.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Method 2 - Name Change Over Phone</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>For some travelers, it is easy to connect with airline officials directly through a call. For this, a customer can reach out to officials by calling on toll-free or customer care. The toll-free customer service number provided by Spirit Airlines is&nbsp;{{PHONE_NUMBER}}. They can help you understand the&nbsp;<strong>flight name change&nbsp;</strong>process for Spirit Airlines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The airport officials will ask you to provide booking details, including PNR or e-ticket number. Then, the agent will ask you about the rectifications you want to make to your name details. You may have to submit a few documents relating to the name change if needed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you provide the necessary information and legal documents supporting the change, you will get an email confirmation regarding the name change. If you are confused and want any help with the name change process, contact us at {{PHONE_NUMBER}}.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Method 3 - Name Change at the Airport</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Spirit Airlines offers an additional offline option to make corrections in the first, last, or middle name. In this method, you need to visit the airport to modify the name on the reservation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the reservation</strong> through this method, a passenger has to connect with the authorities and disclose the reason for contacting them. Thus, the airport officials will tell the passenger about the name change process for Spirit Airlines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are choosing this method, you must know that it may take longer than usual to change the name on the flight ticket. So, you must reach the airport long before the flight departure time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Essential Documents for Spirit Airlines Flight Name Change&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Spirit Airlines or any other airline will never complete the name change request of a passenger without getting the required documents. These legal documents are a vital aspect of the name change process. In certain circumstances, the production of legal documents is not required. However, in other cases, a customer has to produce the following documents:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Marriage certificate</li>\r\n	<li>Court Order</li>\r\n	<li>Divorce decree</li>\r\n	<li>Other supporting documents for modifying the legal name</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Spirit Airlines Name Correction on the Ticket Charges</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Spirit Airlines may or may not charge any fee for the name change. The charges for the name modification depend on the different conditions. The fee amount also varies depending on several factors. There is no specific structure for name change charges.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any kind of name correction within 24 hours of ticket booking will be free of cost. If you apply for a name change after 24 hours, there will be a fee depending on the type of name change.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-10-29 14:05:42', '2022-10-31 18:31:11'),
(12, 10, NULL, 'JetBlue Airlines Name Change Policy', 'jetblue-airlines-name-change-policy', 'If you have made mistakes in the ticket while booking a JetBlue Airlines flight, donât worry about it. JetBlueâs name change policy facilitates you in modifying the wrong essentials of your name. An inappropriate name can be on the ticket due to incorrect spelling or an inverted name.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Sometimes, a passenger may also request&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> due to marriage, divorce, or other legal instances. The JetBlue Airlines name change policy makes it simpler for a passenger to rectify the name.&nbsp;</p><h2>JetBlue Airlines Name Change Policy Rules</h2><p>Every airline has different policies to help their passengers with name errors. Likewise, JetBlueâs name change policy provides some rules that a traveler must satisfy to request a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>. These conditions apply to first, middle, and last name-related concerns.&nbsp;</p><p>Here are the conditions that you must meet before applying for a name correction or change:</p><ul><li>A passenger who has bought the ticket from JetBlue directly or its associates can be eligible for the name correction.&nbsp;</li><li>A traveler can make changes or corrections to the original PNR. Else, you have to initiate a new booking with a renewed PNR.&nbsp;</li><li>The customer is only allowed to have one reissue of the ticket. Therefore, you must be cautious of the corrections you are making. Review the details thoroughly before submitting them again.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Name correction on the ticket</strong> will require a traveler to submit their âNAMECARTâ number.&nbsp;</li><li>A passenger has to submit the legal documents to process the request for a JetBlue name change. The legal papers must be government-verified to prove the authenticity of the information provided.&nbsp;</li><li>The JetBlue Airlines name change policy allows you to correct or change the nickname, last name, middle name, add first names, etc.&nbsp;</li><li>A passenger can change the details of their name in case of marriage, divorce, and adoption.&nbsp;</li></ul><h2>JetBlue Name Correction on the Tickets Terms</h2><p>A passenger sometimes inadvertently adds incorrect details to the name on the reservation. In such cases, the name change policy of JetBlue Airlines guides travelers on how to alter the name on the air ticket. Before using the name policy, there are a few terms that a customer must be aware of in advance.&nbsp;</p><p>Some of the essential terms of the name change policy are mentioned below:</p><ul><li>A passenger can make corrections in the name in terms of characters only. The character limit will be confirmed by the airline. However, the character limit may vary as per the customerâs name.&nbsp;</li><li>The JetBlue Airlines name change policy does not allow a passenger to change a name that is intentionally written wrong to transfer it to someone else. An airline will not acknowledge such intent.&nbsp;</li><li>A customer may have to pay a fee for a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>.&nbsp;</li></ul><h2>How to Change Name on JetBlue Airlines Ticket?</h2><p>A traveler can use different methods for name change provided under the name change policy of JetBlue Airlines. You can use either online or offline mode at your convenience. You can consider any of the following methods for name corrections on JetBlue air tickets:</p><h3>Method 1 - JetBlue Airlines Name Change via the Website</h3><p>The online method of using the website for name modifications is simple. A passenger can use this mode for&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong> at any hour. You can do quick name rectifications through this method. A passenger has to go through the following steps for a name change:</p><ul><li>Open the official website of JetBlue Airlines on the browser.</li><li>Navigate the âMy Tripsâ section on the Homepage.</li><li>A page will open where you need to fill in your reservation details, including the confirmation code and last name.&nbsp;</li><li>After providing the necessary information, click on the âFind Flightâ button.&nbsp;</li><li>Select the trip and tap on the âModifyâ option.</li><li>Pick the âJetBlue Change Name Onlineâ option to modify the name.&nbsp;</li><li>Do the necessary changes and submit the legal papers in support of the change.</li><li>Complete the form and tap on the âContinueâ button.</li><li>Complete the process by making the payment as mentioned by the airline.&nbsp;</li><li>Print the new boarding pass with the correct details.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>In the case of a name change due to marriage, adoption, or divorce, you may have to give a waiver code.&nbsp;</p><p>The&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong> online option will be available to passengers who will comply with the following conditions:</p><ul><li>A passenger can make single-letter corrections or changes online.</li><li>A traveler can make modifications only to the name. No alterations in dates, cabin classes, or itinerary codes are allowed.</li><li>The change of date of birth is not permitted while correcting the name on your reservation.&nbsp;</li><li>If you want to cancel your reservation and buy a new one with the correct details, purchase the ticket for the same class.&nbsp;</li></ul><h3>Method 2 - JetBlue Airlines Name Change via Customer Care</h3><p>There is an offline mode available for JetBlue&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong>. Under this method, you can call the customer care number and connect with the airlineâs agents. To contact the JetBlue Airlines customer service agents, you can use this number +1-800-538-2583.&nbsp;</p><p>The offline method is preferably best for making crucial modifications. A passenger can make changes to the middle or last name on call. Upon calling, you will be assisted as per your requirement. Then, tell the agents about the corrections that you want to make. Also, mention the reason for the change.&nbsp;</p><p>The airline representative will ask you about the booking details. After that, the agent will ask you to provide legal documents, flight tickets, passports, certificates, etc., if required. Lastly, the airline will process the name change request accordingly and confirm the new boarding pass.&nbsp;</p><p>If you need quick assistance with JetBlueâs name change policy, you can contact us at +1-800-865-1848.</p><h3>Method 3 - JetBlue Airline Name Change via Mobile App</h3><p><strong>Name correction on the reservation</strong> through the mobile app is another online method. A passenger can use the app to change the name on the JetBlue air ticket. The JetBlue mobile application guides the traveler throughout the name correction process and answers queries.&nbsp;</p><p>Customers need to download the app from the Play Store, App Store, or any other site, as mentioned by the airline. You can go along with the following steps for making changes to the JetBlue air ticket:</p><ul><li>First, sign in on the JetBlue mobile app.</li><li>Second, pick up the âJetBlue Manage Bookingâ option.&nbsp;</li><li>Third, provide the reservation details, like name, ticket number, etc.</li><li>Fourth, choose the change or correction you want to make, whether in flight name, seat, etc. Then, select the âchange nameâ option accordingly.</li><li>Fifth, make the changes or corrections by following the directions.</li><li>Last, confirm the changes and request a new reservation with your correct name.&nbsp;</li></ul><h3>Method 4 - JetBlue Airlines Name Change via Live Chat</h3><p>A few passengers would definitely like to use the live chat option for&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the reservation</strong>. To avail of this option, you can go to JetBlueâs official website. Look for the âcontact usâ option. Upon selecting, you will get multiple ways to resolve your concerns regarding the name change. Out of them, choose the live chat option.&nbsp;</p><p>A window will open where you can share your concern. Next, the chatbox will ask you to provide your profile details. For this, there will be a link. By using that link, you can update your information.&nbsp;</p><h3>Method 5 - JetBlue Airlines Name Change via Social Media</h3><p>JetBlue Airlines has provided its travelers with one more option for name correction on their tickets. With the help of this method, a passenger can readily mention the query and share it. The JetBlue Airlines team remains vigilant and works on the&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> quickly. Therefore, this name change method resolves the query quicker than any other mode.&nbsp;</p><p>For a name change under this method, you need to visit the website and tap on the contact us page. At the bottom of the page, you will find all the social media platforms via which you can reach the airline online. Choose a suitable platform, write your name correction query, and tag the airlineâs official account.&nbsp;</p><p>After some time, you will receive a response regarding your query. By following the directions given by the airlines, you will get the details amended or changed in the stipulated time.&nbsp;</p><h2>What is JetBlue Airlines Name Change Fees?</h2><p>A traveler can only make one change per passenger. If you want to modify your name more than once, you will have to pay a fee. The charge depends on multiple factors. However, the average fee charged by JetBlue Airlines can be:</p><ul><li>Blue Basic seat holders may have to pay $100. The charge may extend to $200 on flights other than the USA, Mexico, or Central America.&nbsp;</li><li>Under JetBlue\'s name change policy, travelers traveling with Blue, Blue Extra, Blue Refundable, Blue Plus, Blue Plus Refundable, Mint, and Mint Refundable can alter changes by paying fare differences.&nbsp;</li><li>A passenger using offline mode for&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> will be required to pay $50 or more, depending on the fare type.&nbsp;</li><li>The cost may vary in case of a name change due to marriage, adoption, or divorce.&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-10-29 14:10:09', '2022-10-29 14:10:09'),
(13, 10, NULL, 'Volaris Airlines Name Change Policy', 'volaris-airlines-name-change-policy', 'Every airline requires a passenger to fly with correct details. If the flyer provides incorrect information that doesnât match the details on their government-issued identity cards, it may land them in trouble. In this event, the name change policy of Volaris Airlines helps them to come out of this problem.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>With the help of this policy, a traveler can request&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the tickets</strong> of Volaris airlines.&nbsp;</p><p>The name change policy is a set of guidelines that directs the passenger to modify the name on the air ticket. It has specified the situations when a traveler can apply for name corrections under this policy. To know how it can be helpful for your journey ahead with Volaris Airlines, continue reading.&nbsp;</p><h2>Volaris Airlines Name Correction Policy</h2><p>A passenger can use the Volaris Airlines name correction policy in the case of an incorrect name on the booking. But a passenger should know the airline policy before requesting&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the reservation</strong>. If you want to alter the details on the ticket, you must understand the following circumstances:</p><ul><li>A traveler cannot request name corrections on the same day as the scheduled departure.&nbsp;</li><li>The name change will not be allowed for other flights in the case of multiple airlines or interline agreement partners. Only Volaris Airlines ticket correction will be permitted.</li><li>A customerâs scheduled departure should not be within 24 hours of the name change request.&nbsp;</li><li>A person who has already taken the outbound flight should not be allowed to request&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong>.&nbsp;</li></ul><h2>Volaris Airlines Name Change Policy Guidelines</h2><p>A passenger may face boarding denial if the details donât match the name on their government-verified identity card. However, using the guidelines of Volaris Airlines name change policy, you can request the name change:</p><ul><li>Minor modifications in the first, middle, or last name are allowed.</li><li>If passengers alter their name due to marriage or separation, they may submit legal documents supporting the reasons for change.&nbsp;</li><li>The Volaris name change policy doesnât allow a traveler to change the ticket from one person to another. In that case, the passenger has to cancel the previous ticket and rebook again.&nbsp;</li><li>A person can use offline or online methods to request&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on the reservation</strong>.&nbsp;</li><li>The passengers can modify up to 4 characters in the last, middle, or first name.&nbsp;</li><li>A passenger will have to pay a non-refundable fee of 200 dollars along with the fare differences if any.&nbsp;</li></ul><h2>Volaris Airlines Name Change Request Types</h2><p>The name change policy of Volaris Airlines allows certain types of name modification on the ticket. As per the Volaris policy, the following types of name change requests can be allowed:</p><ul><li>A traveler can request a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong> in the event of marriage. After the request, the airlines will re-issue the ticket to a similar or higher-class service, subject to availability.&nbsp;</li><li>A passenger can alter the name on the ticket due to legal reasons. For this, the customer has to submit all the legal papers, like a new photo identity card with an updated name and legal decree.&nbsp;</li><li>Volaris Airlines allows the correction of spelling errors for up to four characters on the middle, first, or last name.&nbsp;</li><li>The name change policy of this airline also permits the addition or elimination of the middle or last name. You can also apply for a name change if you have two last names.</li></ul><p>In all these cases, a passenger is allowed to apply for a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>. However, a passenger must see if the details on the reservation are identical to the passport or any other government ID.&nbsp;</p><h2>How to Request Name Change on Volaris Airlines Ticket?</h2><p>Volaris Airlines provides various options for modifying the name on the flight ticket. Passengers can choose any method that suits their needs. Following are the ways that a traveler can use to rectify a name:</p><h3>1. Method I - Name Change via Website</h3><p>A Volaris Airlines passenger can use the online method to correct the name on the ticket. It is the most used mode of name alterations. A traveler can use this online method anytime, as it is available 24 hours a day. A customer should look into the following steps to make the necessary changes to the air ticket:</p><ul><li>First, a traveler should open the Volaris Airlines official website.</li><li>Second, find the âMy Tripsâ option on the website and click on it.</li><li>Third, fill in the blank spaces with the correct name and reservation number.</li><li>Fourth, select the concerned flight from the list of flights.&nbsp;</li><li>Fifth, click on the edit and make the required changes.</li><li>Sixth, pay a fee if any.</li><li>Seventh, send the request for change after making the payment.</li><li>Lastly, the airline will mail the revised ticket that includes the correct name of the passenger.&nbsp;</li></ul><h3>2. Method II - Name Change via Airport Counter</h3><p>Under the name change policy, a passenger having a Volaris Airlines ticket can modify the name through the airport counter. For this, you have to visit the airport. After visiting the airport, you must go to the Volaris ticket counter for&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong>. Further, the staff will guide you to the name change counter.&nbsp;</p><p>At the name change counter, an agent will be available to facilitate you with the name change process. Ask them for name modification and show them all the original legal documents. Later, Volaris Airlines will examine the documents. The carrier will ask for payment if any fees will apply to you.&nbsp;</p><p>After the successful payment, the airline will make the corrections and send you a mail about the name change.&nbsp;</p><h3>3. Method III - Name Change via Phone Call</h3><p>Some travelers want to make changes while sitting at their homes. The calling method is the most convenient and authentic offline mode of&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the reservation</strong>. A passenger can call the customer care number, which is +1 866 988-3527. It is the toll-free number of the airline. Dial this number and connect with Volaris Airlines.&nbsp;</p><p>Once you are connected to the airline, the agent will ask for a booking code. After that, request the representative for name modifications. If the corrections are possible, the agent will ask you to provide the reservation details. Here, you have to give your authentic identity details. Afterward, the agent will ask you to pay some fees if applicable. Once you made the payment, the agent will confirm the modification on the ticket in the mail.&nbsp;</p><h3>4. Method IV - Name Change via Email Service</h3><p>Volaris Airlines has provided email service to its passengers for a&nbsp;<strong>name change on the boarding pass</strong>. With the help of mail, a passenger can easily alter the name on the ticket. The mail service may not guarantee instant changes. Still, if you want to use this method, you can write your query to the carrier via mail.&nbsp;</p><p>In the query, you must mention the reservation code and last name. After that, send the mail to the official email Id of the airline. Afterward, you need to wait for the response. Once you hear back from them, check whether the name has changed or not.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: If you face any difficulty while using any of the above methods, you can contact us at this number +1-800-865-1848.</p><h2>Volaris Airlines Name Change Limitations</h2><p>In most cases, the policy doesnât allow a passenger to change the name. So, a traveler must know the following limitations to understand the Volaris Airlines name change policy:</p><ul><li>The adults cannot transfer their reservation to a child or senior citizen. Volaris Airlines doesnât allow such change.&nbsp;</li><li>The name change is not permitted if the passenger has purchased the ticket using Volaris digital credits.&nbsp;</li></ul><h2>Volaris Airlines Fees for Name Corrections on the Ticket</h2><p>Every airline charges some fees for modifying the name on the ticket. Similarly, Volaris Airlines also ask the passenger to pay some amount for correcting the name. The fees charged by this carrier are very nominal. The cost of fees is evaluated by factors like the class of ticket, location of the trip, and other information. Volaris Airlines name change fee ranges from $0 to $400.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-10-29 14:14:44', '2022-10-29 18:51:40'),
(14, 10, NULL, 'Hawaiian Airlines Name Change Policy', 'hawaiian-airlines-name-change-policy', 'Name errors on the ticket are usual phenomena. A passenger tends to make minor to major mistakes while booking the ticket. However, an airline keeps all these blunders in mind and facilitates its travelers with name change policies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Like any other airline, Hawaiian Airlines also has a name change policy to help passengers with certain modifications.&nbsp;</p><p>Therefore, you can make&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on a ticket,&nbsp;</strong>whether it arises due to marriage, divorce, adoption, or spelling mistakes. The Hawaiian Airlines name change policy aims to direct the passengers to name corrections. Thus, a traveler of Hawaiian must know about the name change policy and other guidelines.&nbsp;</p><h2>Hawaiian Airlines Name Change Policy Conditions</h2><p>Before using the Hawaiian Airlines name change policy, you must understand it thoroughly. Under this policy, a flyer can change or add to the last name, change the legal name, or shift the first and middle name. To make&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on the reservation</strong>, you will need to follow a different process for each type of change. The airlines will provide you with plausible methods after considering the nature of the change.</p><p>Although Hawaiian Airlines permits several corrections in the name, it still imposes certain conditions on a passenger. So, you must follow these conditions to take advantage of the name change policy.&nbsp;</p><p>Here are the following eligibility regulations of the name change policy:</p><ul><li>The ticket on which you want to make modifications must be bought directly from Hawaiian Airlines.</li><li>All the passenger\'s tickets must contain 13 digits as their code.&nbsp;</li><li>The first three digits on the ticket must start with 173. If it isnât the case with you, you will have to contact the airline.&nbsp;</li><li>A passenger can change the name due to marriage, divorce, and adoption.&nbsp;</li><li>The modifications in the middle name are possible depending on the purpose.</li><li>Travelers are allowed to change their nickname to their full name if they meet the necessary criteria.&nbsp;</li><li>According to the Hawaiian name change policy, an error of up to three characters in the name is considered to be a minor modification. The mistake of more than three characters will be assumed to be a name change.&nbsp;</li></ul><h2>Documents Required for Name Change</h2><p>Modifying or changing the name is not simple. A passenger must submit the necessary documents for certain types of name changes. These legal papers are proof of your modification or name change. These documents held great importance in the case of marriage, divorce, or legal change in government name.&nbsp;</p><p>Following is the list of documents that you must submit during the&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong> of Hawaiian Airlines:</p><ul><li>In the case of marriage, a passenger must provide a marriage certificate.</li><li>In the event of divorce, a flyer must submit the divorce decree.&nbsp;</li><li>You must provide a government-issued passport if you want to shift middle or first names.&nbsp;</li><li>If you want to correct the spelling errors, you must show a legal identification document.</li><li>In case of legal name changes, you must provide the court orders.</li></ul><h2>How to Correct Name on Hawaiian Airlines Ticket?</h2><p>There may be a time when you have entered the wrong spelling of your name or forgot to add your last name while booking your reservation. In such cases, it is necessary to make modifications. Hawaiian Airlines facilitate its customers with&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on the reservation</strong> methods.&nbsp;</p><p>Passengers have two ways through which they can alter the wrong name on the Hawaiian ticket:</p><h3>1. Traveler Name Change via Customer Care</h3><p>Hawaiian Airlines offers the name change service via customer care in case of minor errors. You can get in touch with the airline officials on the customer service number. They will guide you step by step to resolve your issue on the ticket.&nbsp;</p><p>Once you connect with the representative, you must give them the reason for your call. Tell them that you want to correct the name on the air ticket. After that, mention the cause of change, like spelling errors, etc. In the case of a misspelling, submitting legal documents is not mandatory. But the agent will check your passport or other government identification certificate before making the corrections.&nbsp;</p><p>After you submit the documents, the process of&nbsp;<strong>name correction on the ticket</strong> will end. Later, you can confirm if they have made the necessary corrections and ask for a new boarding pass with the correct name.&nbsp;</p><h3>2. Passenger Name Change via Online Mode</h3><p>Name correction via online mode is one of the methods to change the name on the ticket. In this method, the website of Hawaiian Airlines will help you correct the name. You can use the following steps to use this method:</p><ul><li>Open the official website of Hawaiian Airlines.&nbsp;</li><li>Find the âManage Flightsâ tab on the home page and click on it.</li><li>You will get four options here, from which you must select âMy Tripsâ.&nbsp;</li><li>On reaching a new page, you must fill in the flight details, including information like the passenger\'s last name, e-ticket number, and confirmation code. If you have forgotten your ticket number, you can retrieve it by clicking on the âForgot Numberâ option on the screen.&nbsp;</li><li>&nbsp;The âView My Tripâ option will help you retrieve your booking.&nbsp;</li><li>Now, choose the reservation on which you want to make corrections. Then, pick the âHawaiian Airlines Change Passenger Nameâ option to perform the modifications.&nbsp;</li><li>Keep following the on-screen directions to finish the&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong> process.&nbsp;</li><li>Pay the name change fee, if any.&nbsp;</li><li>Lastly, take the new boarding pass with the correct information.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>You can send the legal documents in the mail if you have been asked to submit them in support of your name change request. Also, if there is an option available in the online portal to upload the documents, you can use it too.&nbsp;</p><p>If you are facing issues while using these methods, you can contact us at +1-800-865-1848 to accelerate the process of correction.</p><h2>Hawaiian Airlines Legal Name Changes</h2><p>A legal name change is one of the types of name change under the Hawaiian Airlines name change policy. This type of name change includes rectifying the vital part of your name, middle name, or inverted name. The reason for a legal name change can be anything like marriage, divorce, and adoption. Such alterations mainly include additions or eliminations of the last names.&nbsp;</p><p>As a passenger of Hawaiian Airlines, you need to match the details on the boarding pass with your government-issued certificates. If the names don\'t match, you need to make&nbsp;<strong>name corrections on the ticket</strong> before your flight departure. Now, you must be wondering how you can make legal name changes on the reservation. For legal changes, you should take the help of offline mode.&nbsp;</p><p>You can call the customer service number of Hawaiian Airlines to request legal changes in the name. The process for a legal name change through offline mode will be the same as mentioned above.&nbsp;</p><h2>Hawaiian Airlines Name Correction Fee</h2><p>The name correction fee is not fixed. It depends on the factors like correction type, flight type, etc. If you have bought the ticket from a third-party website, then $25 is the approximate charge for a name change. However, the&nbsp;<strong>flight name change</strong> fee may fluctuate between $75-$250 depending on the fare type and destination. If you request a name change before the departure date, you may get a chance to reduce the fee.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-10-29 14:20:05', '2022-10-29 14:20:05');

