(4, 1, 1, 'a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:50:\"How can I change the name on the Southwest ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:187:\"There are three methods of changing the name on the Southwest tickets. A passenger can correct the name by calling the airline officials, using the official website, and a compliant page.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:59:\"Can I request name correction on the ticket after marriage?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:172:\"Yes. A passenger can apply for a name change after marriage. To change the name on the Southwest ticket, you should submit a legal document, such as a marriage certificate.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:78:\"When can I apply for a name change on the boarding pass of Southwest Airlines?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:143:\"You can request a change in the initials of your name when you have made any spelling errors while booking your ticket with Southwest Airlines.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:81:\"What are the charges for name change under Southwest Airlines name change policy?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:195:\"If you request name correction within 24 hours of booking a reservation, there will be no charges to pay. But if you apply for a name change after 24 hours, you will have to pay between $80-$200.\";}}', NULL, '2022-10-14 03:52:14'),
(5, 1, 2, 'a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:82:\"What will happen if I put the incorrect name on the Alaska Airlines flight ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:185:\"Nothing will happen if you request for name change or correction before the scheduled departure. You can use the different methods provided under the Alaska Airlines name change policy.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:43:\"How to change the name on my flight ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:193:\"You can use three methods of name corrections on the ticket under Alaska Airlines name change policy. Passengers can change their name via the website, customer care service, and airport Kiosk.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:72:\"Is there any fee for name corrections on Alaska Airlines flight tickets?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:272:\"The charges for name change or correction depend on when you request the name change on the boarding pass. If you apply for a name change within 24 hours of booking a flight, there will be no charges. However, if you apply after 24 hours, then there will be a fee of $125.\";}}', '2022-10-14 03:57:18', '2022-10-14 05:05:30'),
(6, 1, 5, 'a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:52:\"How to modify the name on the Delta Airlines ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:107:\"A passenger can modify or change the name on the ticket with the help of Delta Airlines name change policy.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:62:\"Can I change my name on the ticket to another personâs name?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:103:\"No. Delta Airlines name change policy doesnât allow a passenger to transfer his name to someone else.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:58:\"How to change the name on my Delta Airlines flight ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:195:\"Delta Airlines name change policy provides three methods for changing the name on the ticket. You can request name correction on the ticket via the official website, phone call, or airport Kiosk.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:66:\"What are the charges for a name change on a Delta Airlines ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:216:\"If you request a name change within 24 hours of booking a ticket, there will be no charge. But if you apply for a name change after 24 hours, you may have to pay between $75-$500, depending on the type of correction.\";}}', '2022-10-14 05:04:30', '2022-10-14 05:04:30'),
(7, 1, 6, 'a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:16:\"This is question\";s:6:\"answer\";s:9:\"xcsdsdsdf\";}}', '2022-10-14 06:42:47', '2022-10-14 06:42:47'),
(8, 1, 7, 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:51:\"Can I cancel my flight within 24 hours of purchase?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:185:\"Yes. A passenger can cancel the ticket within 24 hours if the ticket has been purchased one week before the departure date. In this case, you will get a full refund on your reservation.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:61:\"How can I cancel the reservation of a United Airlines flight?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:136:\"There are three different ways of canceling the air ticket. Such as canceling flights via the website, phone number, and at the airport.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:53:\"Can I cancel my United Airlines flight without a fee?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:280:\"Yes. You can cancel the ticket without paying a cancellation fee. If you cancel the ticket within 24 hours of purchase, no cancellation fee will apply to you. Additionally, you donât have to pay if your flight is delayed by three or more hours and you have canceled that flight.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:53:\"How much do I have to pay for my flight cancellation?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:120:\"In the case of refundable and non-refundable tickets, you will pay $200 for domestic and $400 for international flights.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:59:\"Does United Airlines pay compensation for canceled flights?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:161:\"Yes. United Airlines pay compensation to passengers if their flights get canceled. The compensation amount will depend on the time, cause of delay, and location.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:40:\"Do United Airlines cancel flights often?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:235:\"No. United Airlines doesnât cancel flights often. They cancel the flights only when there is some unprecedented reason. The purpose of cancellation can be anything like a natural disaster, a weather issue, covid-19 restrictions, etc.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:41:\"When do United Airlines pay compensation?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:181:\"United Airlines pays compensation when there is a flight delay or cancellation due to any reason. In such cases, the passenger will either get compensation or an alternative flight.\";}}', '2022-10-21 18:32:56', '2022-10-21 20:16:34'),
(9, 1, 11, 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:49:\"Can I change the name on Spirit Airlines tickets?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:154:\"Yes. You can modify the name on the ticket if there is any error. There are three methods by which a passenger can request name corrections on the ticket.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:90:\"How many misspelled letters or characters of my first, last, or middle name can I correct?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:79:\"You can modify a maximum of three letters of your first, middle, and last name.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:53:\"How to correct the name of my Spirit Airlines ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:117:\"You can use different methods of a name change on the boarding pass of Spirit Airlines as per the name change policy.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:85:\"Can I use the official website of Spirit Airlines to correct the initials in my name?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:104:\"Yes. A passenger can take the help of Spirit Airlines official website to change the name on the ticket.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:44:\"What is the Spirit Airlines name change fee?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:184:\"The name change fee depends on multiple factors. There are set rules for name change fees. You can contact the Spirit Airlines center and get the information about the name change fee.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:65:\"Can I change the name on the Spirit Airlines reservation offline?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:241:\"Yes. You can initiate the offline request for a name change on the Spirit Airlines ticket. The airline authority will help you with the name change process. For this, you need to call on the toll-free customer care number of Spirit Airlines.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:51:\"What are the essential documents for a name change?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:166:\"A passenger may need to submit documents in case of marriage, divorce, or adoption. Therefore, you must have a marriage certificate, divorce decree, court order, etc.\";}}', '2022-10-29 14:35:00', '2022-10-29 14:35:00'),
(10, 1, 12, 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:59:\"Can I modify my name on the JetBlue Airlines flight ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:108:\"Yes. You can alter any type of name error in JetBlueâs air ticket with the help of its name change policy.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:88:\"What are the options for name change available under JetBlueâs name correction policy?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:208:\"There are five methods of name corrections on the ticket under the name change policy of JetBlue. The passengers can rectify their name via the website, social media, customer care, mobile app, and live chat.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:46:\"Does JetBlue charge any fee for a name change?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:132:\"The fee for name change can vary depending on various factors. However, the charges start from $50 and can include fare differences.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:43:\"How can I change my wrong name on a flight?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:133:\"You can consider the name change policy of JetBlue. In this policy, several methods of name correction are provided that you can use.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:46:\"Can I change my last name on JetBlue Airlines?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:95:\"Yes. You can change your last name on JetBlue Airlines with the help of the name change policy.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:91:\"Can I transfer my ticket to another person with the help of the JetBlue name change policy?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:145:\"No. You cannot transfer your ticket reservation to someone elseâs name. JetBlueâs name change policy doesnât allow the transfer of tickets.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:68:\"How can I change my name on the JetBlue ticket through social media?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:250:\"It is easy to change your name through social media. JetBlueâs team is active on social media. You can visit the Contact Us page on the website, where you can find social media icons. By tapping on those icons, you can write your name change query.\";}}', '2022-10-29 14:43:01', '2022-10-29 14:43:01'),
(11, 1, 13, 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:59:\"Can I correct the name on the Volaris Airlines reservation?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:169:\"Yes. You can apply for a name change on the Volaris Airlines air ticket. There are four methods of adding a name, eliminating a character, or correcting spelling errors.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:56:\"How much does Volaris Airlines cost for name correction?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:220:\"The cost of name correction on the ticket depends on several factors, including the type of name change request, the location of the trip, and other factors. However, the charges for a name change may range from $0-$200.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:45:\"Can I transfer my Volaris ticket to my child?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:133:\"No. You cannot transfer your ticket to a child or a senior citizen. Volaris Airlines will not allow the change of name in such cases.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:79:\"Do I have to pay any fee if I request a name change within 24 hours of booking?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:118:\"No. You will not have to pay any fee if you request a name change on the boarding pass within 24 hours of reservation.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:81:\"What is the procedure I need to follow for name correction on the Volaris ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:216:\"Volaris Airlines offers numerous ways for customers to change the name on the reservation. They can contact the airline directly through a toll-free number, use the website for name correction, and visit the airport.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:58:\"Can I change my legal name on the Volaris Airlines ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:127:\"Yes. You can change your legal name on the ticket. However, you need to provide the legal documents supporting the name change.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:82:\"Does the name on the booking must match the government-issued identification card?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:56:\"Yes. Your name must match the name on the government ID.\";}}', '2022-10-29 14:46:39', '2022-10-29 14:46:39'),
(12, 1, 14, 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:79:\"What are the methods of name change under Hawaiian Airlines name change policy?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:140:\"There are two methods available for changing the name on the ticket. Passengers can use either offline or online modes at their convenience.\";}i:1;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:64:\"How can I change my name on the Hawaiian Airlines flight ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:212:\"You can correct the name on your air ticket with the help of two options given under the name change policy of Hawaiian Airlines. One is through a customer service number, and another is via the official website.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:58:\"What are the flight name change fees of Hawaiian Airlines?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:271:\"The flight name change fees depend on several factors, including correction type, fare type, the destination of the flight, etc. In case of a ticket bought from a third-party website, you will need to pay a fixed amount of $25. Otherwise, the charges range from $75-$250.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:88:\"Do I require to submit the legal documents for a name change due to marriage or divorce?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:109:\"Yes. In case of a name change due to legal reasons, you must submit a marriage certificate or divorce decree.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:81:\"What kind of name changes are allowed under Hawaiian Airlines name change policy?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:148:\"Under the Hawaiian Name change policy, any additions or changes to the last name, legal name change, and shifting of middle & last name are allowed.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:57:\"What are the name change conditions in Hawaiian Airlines?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:138:\"The ticket must be bought from Hawaiian Airlines directly. A passenger can change the name in the case of divorce, marriage, and adoption.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:8:\"question\";s:73:\"What documents should I have to submit for name correction on the ticket?\";s:6:\"answer\";s:118:\"A passenger must submit a marriage certificate, divorce decree, government-issued passport, court orders, and ID card.\";}}', '2022-10-29 14:50:08', '2022-10-29 14:50:08');

